high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen counter
grab a sponge out from the cabinet above
look down at the pot on the kitchen counter
place the sponge in the pot on the kitchen counter
pick up the pot off of the kitchen counter
turn around and walk over to the counter to the right of the the stove
place the pot in a cabinet to the bottom right of the kitchen stove
anns.task_desc: place a pot with a sponge in it in a kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight to the counter with the pot on it.
Open the top right cabinet and take out the sponge.
Look down at the pot.
Place the sponge in the pot.
Pick up the pot.
Look down at the cabinets under the counter.
Place the pot in the bottom right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a sponge in it in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight ahead, to the counter with the pot on it.
Above the counter, open the cabinet and remove the sponge.
Go back down to the counter below.
Put the sponge in the pot on the counter.
Pick up the pot on the counter.
Turn around, turn left, then turn around to face the stove.
Open the cabinet near the stove and place the pot inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a sponge in it in the cabinet.
